---
title: Jon Connington
---

Lord Jon Connington, Lord of Griffin's Roost, was the head of House Connington and for a time Hand of the King. He was one of the few close friends of Rhaegar Targaryen. He had no brothers. Connington is clean shaven with leathery skin and crow's feet at the corners of his eyes, his greying red hair is dyed blue when under the alias of "Griff". 


